92
00:07:23,943 --> 00:07:25,945
He said you

93
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:28,381
were hardworking.

94
00:07:29,248 --> 00:07:30,716
What else?

95
00:07:31,851 --> 00:07:34,554
That's it.

96
00:07:37,523 --> 00:07:39,759
