97
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:41,961
can't be summed up in a few words.

98
00:07:41,961 --> 00:07:43,796
Just like only I know

99
00:07:43,796 --> 00:07:45,665
that he doesn't like others

100
00:07:45,665 --> 00:07:47,934
messing up his desk like this.

101
