116
00:08:29,542 --> 00:08:30,843
What about you?

117
00:08:30,843 --> 00:08:32,144
Do you have some photos

118
00:08:32,144 --> 00:08:34,213
with the professor at home?

119
00:08:36,816 --> 00:08:38,251
I don't.

120
00:08:39,819 --> 00:08:41,354
No?

121
