129
00:08:58,104 --> 00:08:59,205
Look at this.

130
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,642
Professor, you're back.

131
00:09:02,642 --> 00:09:04,410
Is there anything you need help with?

132
00:09:04,410 --> 00:09:05,845
Not really.

133
00:09:10,216 --> 00:09:11,417
I'm sorry.

134
00:09:11,417 --> 00:09:13,252
