137
00:09:16,055 --> 00:09:17,423
So…

138
00:09:19,825 --> 00:09:20,893
Not for others,

139
00:09:20,893 --> 00:09:22,295
but you're an exception.

140
00:09:31,537 --> 00:09:32,772
