153
00:10:13,946 --> 00:10:14,947
Do we do this?

154
00:10:19,702 --> 00:10:25,152
♫ If I'm not as kind as you imagined ♫

155
00:10:25,782 --> 00:10:29,760
♫ Would you then overturn ♫

156
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:32,899
♫ Your faith in love ♫

157
00:10:34,036 --> 00:10:36,480
♫ Has anyone not ever been lost ♫

158
00:10:37,718 --> 00:10:40,511
♫ In the vast ocean of humanity ♫

159
00:10:40,918 --> 00:10:43,656
♫ Awaking towards the light of dreams ♫

160
00:10:44,214 --> 00:10:46,034
♫ A grand dream is all it is ♫

161
