Professor.

162
00:10:51,951 --> 00:10:53,419
Professor.

163
00:10:53,419 --> 00:10:55,154
Congratulations on your award.

164
00:10:55,154 --> 00:10:56,689
Just put it in the cabinet.

165
00:11:00,059 --> 00:11:01,127
Right, Professor,

166
00:11:01,127 --> 00:11:03,095
