167
00:11:03,095 --> 00:11:05,498
should it be uploaded by now?

168
00:11:05,498 --> 00:11:07,233
I'm afraid it won't be able to keep up
with their upcoming schedule.

169
00:11:07,233 --> 00:11:08,734
I uploaded it yesterday
after I finished grading it.

170
00:11:08,734 --> 00:11:10,136
Don't trouble yourself.

171
